name: Ordinal Quest
description: Ordinal Quest is a game series built for everyone and featuring BTC Ordinals as Heroes, NPCs, Objects, & more! This game series will act as an onboarding mechanism for everyone outside of blockchain, crypto, and digital collectibles, as well as, provide everyone already inside of those things with a fun and engaging experience. Aside from the Ordinal Quest game series, Ordinal Quest Inscriptions will also be playable on the Digital Collectible PvP platform PFP Pit Brawl (https://pfppb.io). Holders will be able to connect their wallet, select their hero and battle!
